  "statement": "A conversational front door, backed by a headless discovery agent. The app SHALL provide a chat that is backed by a **headless agent** (a `claude -p` / discovery agent) driven over the **same stream bridge** as the two-way chat (FR-16..FR-26), used for onboarding and for starting changes from intent. - *Acceptance:* The discovery chat sends prompts and streams replies through the same relay path as FR-16/FR-17 (no second, parallel bridge is introduced); a test asserts the discovery agent is driven via the existing stream-json bridge",
